\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 Unqualified\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Week 1 - I am __________\
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 ME\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 Illustration of me driving to get yelled at by someone because of things I actually did\'85the whole time I kept thinking I\'92m not like other pastors\'85they\'92re nice and approachable and great at hospital visits and just seem so much more spiritual than me.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I started to come up with labels for myself\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am Intense \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am Intimidating\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am Cold \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am impatient\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am unreasonable\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am a failure\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am unqualified for this\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition: \'a0You ever think about yourself like that?  Give yourself a label?\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe everyone labels themselves all the time\'85it\'92s what we do in life\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Yours may or may not be the same as mine but here goes a list of some\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Loser\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Failure\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Bad Parent\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Bad Spouse\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Ungrateful\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Addict \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Dysfunctional\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Deficient\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Forgetful\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Late\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not good with numbers or details\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Pathetic\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Immoral\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Liar\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jerk\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Unlovable\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We label ourselves so much but what I want you to know is this today\'85\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your label is your limitation\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The labels you put on yourself or you allow others to put on you is the limitation you accept on your life \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We talk ourselves out of so many things before they even begin\'85just because of a label.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  But what if the mistakes of the Bible were recorded not as a warning but as an encouragement.  \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(setup the passage a little)\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 12\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Looking this way and that and seeing no one, he killed the Egyptian and hid him in the sand.\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 13\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The next day he went out and saw two Hebrews fighting. He asked the one in the wrong, \'93Why are you hitting your fellow Hebrew?\'94\
\

\f3\b\fs18 \super 14\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The man said, \'93Who made you ruler and judge over us?\'a0Are you thinking of killing me as you killed the Egyptian?\'94 Then Moses was afraid and thought, \'93What I did must have become known.\'94  Exodus 2\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The guy ask \'96 who do you think you are?  Label!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You think you\'92re qualified to lead us?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When we aren\'92t clear on the answer or we mess up it can make us doubt all we hold onto as true.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And so he leaves behind his destiny and goes into the desert\'85stuck\'85for 40 years of his life.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How many of us feel stuck because we\'92ve tried to put God on hold or what He\'92s calling us to on hold?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 2\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub There the angel of the\'a0Lord\'a0appeared to him in flames of fire\'a0from within a bush.\'a0Moses saw that though the bush was on fire it did not burn up.\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 3\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So Moses thought, \'93I will go over and see this strange sight\'97why the bush does not burn up.\'94\
\

\f3\b\fs18 \super 4\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When the\'a0Lord\'a0saw that he had gone over to look, God called\'a0to him from within the bush,\'a0\'93Moses! Moses!\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He says a few things but a few verses later we get to the point\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 10\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So now, go. I am sending\'a0you to Pharaoh to bring my people the Israelites out of Egypt.\'94\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Big call on his life right?  God is going to send him to do the VERY thing he wanted to do a little while ago\'85what do you think Moses response would be?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t you think he would be excited, motivated\'85finally someone believes in me and it\'92s GOD of all people!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 11\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But Moses said to God, \'93Who am I\'a0that I should go to Pharaoh and bring the Israelites out of Egypt?\'94  \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Did you catch that\'85Who am I?  It is the very same question someone asked him to make him leave originally.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He doesn\'92t know who he is.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He\'92s stuck in the desert avoiding his destiny for 40 years because of this.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Someone else put a label on Moses 40 years earlier\'8540 YEARS!  And when God Himself asks him to do something the first thing all Moses can think of is, is what someone else said first?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your Label is your limitation!  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He has already talked himself out of what God was calling him to do.  Not because God wasn\'92t real, wasn\'92t clear, or wasn\'92t going to help\'85just because he had a label\'85\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am unqualified\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God didn\'92t you hear about what happened the last time I tried this?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He is seeing God, experiencing God, and even hearing directly from God, but is not being changed by God because he can\'92t hear over his lid.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I wonder how many people come to church every week and hear great message and God shows up and they can feel and experience Him in a mighty way only to leave never really changed because the lid is still there?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are people in this room right now who are missing out on all that God would have for you simply because you believe the label of someone else above the label God gives you!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And what lifts the limitation isn\'92t time\'85it\'92s perspective!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92re waiting for time to heal you or time to fix you or whatever\'85Moses had 40 years and it didn\'92t help.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 12\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And God said, \'93I will be with you.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Notice what God doesn\'92t do\'85he doesn\'92t reassure Moses of his own abilities!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He doesn\'92t say NO\'85you\'92re so gifted and great and everyone will believe you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It will be easy\'85you\'92ll have no problems.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He doesn\'92t become a coach like I would want to and encourage him\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He just tells him that \'93I will be with you\'94.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Maybe instead of you thinking God is telling you to go somewhere we need to start thinking God is inviting us to join Him.  It\'92s not so much a \'93You go\'94 but a \'93Come on\'94.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 13\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Moses said to God, \'93Suppose I go to the Israelites and say to them, \'91The God of your fathers has sent me to you,\'92 and they ask me, \'91What is his name?\'92\'a0Then what shall I tell them?\'94\

\f3\b\fs18 \super 14\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub God said to Moses, \'93I am who I am.  This is what you are to say to the Israelites: \'91I am\'a0has sent me to you.\'92\'94  Exodus 3\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why would God give Moses such an ambiguous answer when what he needed most is certainty?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This really bugged me\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But I started thinking about the name\'85I Am\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf7 Transition:  You remember this game we would play when we were kids when someone would call us a name?\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs24 \cf2 Illustration of us telling others as kids \'93I know you are but what am I?\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God tells Moses\'85I know you are but what am I?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92re not telling me anything new about you\'85I made you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know all the insecurities, all of the issues, all of the failures, all of things you struggle with as a human being\'85I know you are\'85BUT WHAT AM I?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve got to quit being so self-indulged and start looking somewhere else!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He says \'96 I KNOW YOU ARE\'85BUT WHAT AM I?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know you\'92re weak\'85but what AM I?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know you\'92re doubtful\'85but what AM I?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is when we realize we are Unqualified\'85and are ok with that\'85and know that is how God made us\'85and believe God is sufficient\'85and know He will never leave us\'85that is when we can move forward!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When we can replace our words with His words\'85\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is saying\'85I\'92m everything you\'92re not!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(RANT HERE)\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am loving\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am the redeemer\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am forgiven\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am confident\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am bold\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am freedom\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am good\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am exalted\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am what you\'92re not\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs24 \cf2 Illustration of me hearing God tell me that in order for Him to build a different kind of church He needed a different kind of pastor!\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So I\'92m unqualified (picture in the background)\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Tell people they can do the same thing and proclaim in boldness\'85I am unqualified too with a picture!\
